data.description: Location, Location, Location! This three beds, two baths plus an den/office home provides easy access to I-19 and is conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. The open floor plan makes this home feel much bigger with plenty of room for a growing family or person with hobbies. Ceramic tile throughout, granite countertops in kitchen and recently painted cabinets, the primary bedroom features a walk-in closet. Ceiling fans in every room and a newer water heater - 2022. Don't miss out on this one!
